overview:
Business and engineering leader with strong track record of success at startup and multi-national high technology companies including Intel, HP and Agilent Technologies and Analogix Semiconductor. Currently President at The Enright Group.

Specialties Successful Leader of product development, marketing & business management. Demonstrated leadership in managing global teams. Strong customer satisfaction and vendor management results. Skilled in organizational development and turn-arounds from startup to mature organizations. Experienced in marketing, finance, legal, IP, and contracts. Broad segment coverage includes CE, PC, servers & telecom. Deep technical background in semiconductors and systems.
